quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,30,"woh din anay wala hai, jab har nafs apne kiye ka phal haazir paye ga khuwa uss ne bhalai ki ho ya buraiee is roz aadmi yeh tamanna kere ga ke kash abhi yeh din is se bohat daur hota! Allah tumhe apne aap se darata hai aur woh apne bundon ka nihayat kher khuwa hai"
3,31,"ae Nabi Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! logon se keh do ke,"" agar tum haqeeqat mein Allah se mohabbat rakhtay ho, to Meer y pairwi ikhtiyar karo, Allah tum se mohabbat kere ga aur tumhari khataon se dar guzar farmaiye ga woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai """
3,32,"unn se kaho ke"" Allah aur rasool ki itaat qubool kar lau"" phir tum agar woh tumhari dawat qubool nah karen, to yaqeenan yeh mumkin nahi hai ke Allah aisay logon se mohabbat kere, jo is ki aur is ke rasool ki itaat se inkaar karte hon"
3,33,Allah ne Aadam aur Nooh aur all ibrahim aur all Imran ko tamam duniya walon par tarjeeh day kar ( apni risalat ke liye ) muntakhib kya tha
3,34,"yeh aik silsilay ke log thay, jo aik dosray ki nasal se peda hue thay Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
3,35,"( woh uss waqt sun raha tha ) jab Imran ki aurat keh rahi thi ke,"" mere parvar-digaar! mein is bachay ko jo mere pait mein hai teri Nazar karti hon, woh tairay hi kaam ke liye waqf hoga meri is peshkash ko qubool farma to suneney aur jan-nay wala hai """
3,36,"phir jab woh bachi is ke haan peda hui to is ne kaha"" maalik! mere haan to larki peda ho gayi hai halaank jo kuch is ne jina tha, Allah ko is ki khabar thi aur larka lar ki ki terhan nahi hota kher, mein ne is ka naam maryam rakh diya hai aur mein usay aur is ki aindah nasal ko shetan mardood ke ftne se teri panah mein deti hon """
3,37,"aakhir kaar is ke Rab ne is larki ko bakhushi qubool farma liya, ussay barri achi larki bana kar uthaya aur Zikria kuaa seen ka sarparast bana diya Zikria jab kabhi is ke paas mahaRab mein jata to is ke paas kuch nah kuch khanay peenay ka samaan paata puchta maryam! yeh tairay pa seen kahan se aaya? woh jawab deti Allah ke paas se aaya hai, Allah jisay chahta hai be hisaab deta hai"
